<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
        background-color: #fff;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
    }
    h1 {
        color: #007bff;
        font-size: 2.4em;
    }
    p {
        color: #666;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .footer {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    }
</style>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome</h1>
        <p>We're excited to have you join our community! As part of the registration process, we've generated a unique code for you.</p>
        <p>Your code: <strong>@ViewData["CodeForAuth"]</strong></p>
        <p>Please use this code to complete your registration. If you didn't request this code, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>